    <h3 align=center id=qname>Bear Hide Armor</h3><hr size=1>
	 <table width=100% cellpadding=3 cellspacing=0 border=0>
	 <tr><td valign=top>
	 <table cellpadding=1 cellspacing=1 border=0 align=left>
	 <tr><td><b>Starts in:</b></td><td><a href='http://everquest.allakhazam.com/zones/Antonica/QeynosH.htm'>Qeynos Hills</a></td></tr>
	 <tr><td><b>Who:</b></td><td><a href=http://eqbeastiary.allakhazam.com/search.shtml?id=2982>Chanda Miller</a></td></tr>
	 <tr><td><b>Rating:</b></td><td>Average (3.96)</td></tr>
	 <tr><td><b>Estimated Time:</b></td><td></td></tr>
	 <tr><td><b>Minimum Level:</b></td><td>8</td></tr><tr><td><b>Best Class:</b></td><td>All</td></tr><tr><td colspan=2><b>Factions Raised:</b><li><a href="http://eqbeastiary.allakhazam.com/faction.html?faction=101">Guards of Qeynos</a></li><li><a href="http://eqbeastiary.allakhazam.com/faction.html?faction=142">Karana Residents</a></li><li><a href="http://eqbeastiary.allakhazam.com/faction.html?faction=102">Knights of Thunder</a></li><li><a href="http://eqbeastiary.allakhazam.com/faction.html?faction=93">Priests of Life</a></li></ul></td></tr><tr><td colspan=2><b>Quest Items:</b></span><li><a href="http://eqdb.allakhazam.com/item.html?item=2735">Bearskin (various qualities)</a></li></ul></td></tr></td></tr></table>Chanda makes bear hide armor.  The better the piece, the more faction you need to get it.<br><br>Bear Hide Belt - 5 GP and Low quality Bear pelt<br><br>Bear Hide Boots - 15 GP and Medium quality<br>bear pelt;<br><br>Bear Hide Cape - 21 GP and High quality bear pelt.<br><br>Buying one of the items also gives you the<br>following faction adjustments: +KaranaResidents, +GuardsofQeynos, +PriestsofLife, +KnightsofThunder </td></tr>
	 <tr><td id=rt valign=top>Reward(s):</td></tr>
	 <tr><td valign=top><li><a href="http://eqdb.allakhazam.com/item.html?item=928">Bear-hide Belt</a></li><li><a href="http://eqdb.allakhazam.com/item.html?item=1753">Bear-hide Boots</a></li><li><a href="http://eqdb.allakhazam.com/item.html?item=2157">Bear-hide Cape</a></li></td></tr>
