	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Decent<span id=notbold>[3.00]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>Playing with my alternate character, Owin, an 8 Barb Rogue, I easily got all 3 pieces of armor, since bear pelts aren't worth much on Vazaelle.  You only need to be lvl 2 to kill the polar bear cubs in Everfrost, not 8 like you need to kill bears in QH, plus I don't kill bears there anyway because of cross treehugger and holly.  Just sneak and hide, or ask a rogue friend to do it for you.  This would sure beat the cloth armor that my main, Iildiin, is wearing, and it might be worth selling someplace else like Felwithe to all the casters. Oh and also Chanda won't talk if hailed so just ask what cloaks, what belts, etc to get the requirements.<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
